overview: This is a live concert for the PBS series Soundstage. Filmed live at WTTW's studio in Chicago, Illinois.  Set List :  Queer,  Bad Boyfriend,  Boys Wanna Fight,  Sex Is Not The Enemy,  I Think I'm Paranoid,  Push It,  Why Do You Love Me?,  Vow,  Stupid Girl,  I'm Only Happy When It Rains,  Right Between The Eyes, Happy Home.
title: Garbage - Live at Soundstage
